    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know it can be risky but i'm not talking about drinking a whole bottle. i just mean like one glass of red wine. if i drink it a little while before or after taking the pill, won't it just kind of boost the effect? it feels like a natural way to help the medicine kick in. surely a tiny bit won't cause the \"life-threatening\" stuff you're talking about?",
