      "content": "honestly the tea and baths don't really do much for my insomnia. i'm just curious about the science of it. since wine is just a relaxant too, doesn't it just make sense that they work together to help me sleep? i'm not looking to get drunk, just trying to see if i can use the wine to make the diazepam more effective so i don't have to take a higher dose of the actual medicine. would that be a way to optimize the treatment?",
